				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>For this weeks Bass Riff of the Week I wanted to pay tribute to one of my favorite bass players Pino Palladino.</p>
<p>Within the riff I'm going to show you various "Pino-ism's" so you can start to slip them into your own bass lines and grooves until they become a solid part of your own vocabulary.</p>
<p>We're going be looking at left hand muting, double stops, and much more...</p>
<p>As always, see you in the shed...</p>
<p>Scott :)</p>
