		<title>How To Add Sexy Notes Into Your Bass Lines &#038; Grooves &#8211; Bass riff of the week #14 (L#139)</title>
		<link>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/riff-of-the-week/sexy-notes-bass-lines-grooves.html</link>
